creator: SC Friends
descriptionHtml:
It's a tool to help you to know what makes you get more followers. Or what caused you lost fans.
Launch mFollowers daily. You will know the number of new followers and lost followers per day.
You can also see the growth trend through the chart. The date option can be 1 day,30 days,90 days...360 days.

Functions List:
1.Following and Followers
2.Not Follow Me Back
3.You not follow back
4.Mutual

We do not collect your social account password.
We do not post anything on your social media.
